snippet.title: PC-98 Longplay - Peret em Heru [English] Horror Survival Game
snippet.description:
Walkthrough of a creepy rpgmaker released in 1998 on PC-98 japanese computer.

Author : Makoto Yaotani 
Music  : Kei Mizuho
